- MP-4151-Order Details-Customer n CSR n Mobile
-- Complete a UK Single Line Delivery Order
-- Go to My Account - Orders & Returns --- Order Number is visible on Order History Page
-- Click Order Number --- Order Details Page is displayed with Order Details Header - Delivery Group Module - Payment Module
